Topics in Advanced General Relativity, by Sergei Winitzki


This is the set of source files for the lecture notes. The text is distributed
under the GNU Free Documentation License (www.gnu.org/copyleft/fdl.html).

The source is maintained using the LyX editor (www.lyx.org).
The LyX source file and the resulting TeX file are provided.

The commands used to create the PDF file are:

Using LyX 1.4.3 or later:
```
lyx --export pdf GR_course.lyx
```
without LyX:
```
latex GR_course.tex (3 times)
makeindex GR_course.idx -o GR_course.ind
latex GR_course.tex
dvips GR_course.dvi
ps2pdf GR_course.ps
```
